---
import SinglePage from "../../layouts/SinglePage.astro";
---

<SinglePage>
  <h1>Contact Us</h1>

  <p>
    We'd love to hear from you! Whether you have a project in mind, need support
    with an existing website, or just want to say hello, we're here and ready to
    help.
  </p>

  <h2>Get in Touch</h2>

  <div>
    <div>
      <h3>📧 Email</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>General Inquiries:</strong><br />
        <a href="mailto:hello@example.com">hello@example.com</a>
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Support:</strong><br />
        <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a>
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Business Partnerships:</strong><br />
        <a href="mailto:partnerships@example.com">partnerships@example.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3>📞 Phone</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>Main Office:</strong><br />
        <a href="tel:+1234567890">+1 (234) 567-8900</a>
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Business Hours:</strong><br />
        Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM PST<br />
        Saturday: 10:00 AM - 4:00 PM PST<br />
        Sunday: Closed
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>📍 Visit Our Office</h2>
  <address>
    <strong>Headquarters</strong><br />
    123 Creative Street<br />
    Design District<br />
    San Francisco, CA 94107<br />
    United States
  </address>

  <h2>💬 Let's Start a Conversation</h2>

  <form class="flex">
    <div>
      <label for="name">Name *</label>
      <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required />
    </div>

    <div>
      <label for="email">Email *</label>
      <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required />
    </div>

    <div>
      <label for="subject">Subject *</label>
      <input type="text" id="subject" name="subject" required />
    </div>

    <div>
      <label for="message">Message *</label>
      <textarea id="message" name="message" required rows="5"></textarea>
    </div>

    <button type="submit"> Send Message </button>
  </form>

  <h2>🌐 Connect With Us</h2>
  <p>
    Follow us on social media for the latest updates, behind-the-scenes content,
    and industry insights:
  </p>

  <ul>
    <li>
      🐦 <a href="https://twitter.com/example">Twitter</a> - Daily tips and industry
      news
    </li>
    <li>
      📘 <a href="https://facebook.com/example">Facebook</a> - Company updates and
      community
    </li>
    <li>
      💼 <a href="https://linkedin.com/company/example">LinkedIn</a> - Professional
      insights and networking
    </li>
    <li>
      📷 <a href="https://instagram.com/example">Instagram</a> - Visual inspiration
      and team highlights
    </li>
    <li>
      💻 <a href="https://github.com/example">GitHub</a> - Open source projects and
      code samples
    </li>
  </ul>

  <div>
    <h3>⚡ Quick Response Promise</h3>
    <p>
      We typically respond to all inquiries within 24 hours during business
      days. For urgent matters, please call our main office number, and we'll
      get back to you as soon as possible.
    </p>
  </div>
</SinglePage>

<style>
  .flex {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  form label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  form input,
  form textarea {
    display: block;
    /* width: 100%; */
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  form div {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  form button {
    max-width: max-content;
  }
</style>
